:4:"text";s:418:"/me chuckled a bit. Noticing her place her things down and then relax on the couch, watching over him. &quot;I guess so. It&#039;s quite frequent for me, but I guess you&#039;ve never had any before, huh?&quot; He asked, a smile on his cute face. &quot;Well, would you like for me to make some Stroganoff? It&#039;s not to hard to cook. Very easy.&quot; He said, lifting up his violin and playing a little bit, softly.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408170071";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081699372";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932657;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932657";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:166:"/me nods, resting her head sideways on the couch a little to get comfortable.[br]&quot;If that would not be too much trouble, yes. Yes I would.&quot; She smiles some.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408170130";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081701616";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932669;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932669";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:365:"/me would set the violin down where he was sitting, giving Fortuna a both tender and teasing kiss on the snout. &quot;You got it then love. One of Granny&#039;s Signature Mushroom Stroganoff.~&quot; He said, trotting to the kitchen and getting prepared. &quot;Unless you are allergic. Really, I can make a stroganoff out of anything. I just prefer Portobello.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408170484";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081703510";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932685;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932685";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:233:"/me shakes her head. &quot;I have no allergies, other than one for &lt;i&gt;stupid&lt;/i&gt;-&quot; She jokes, though it is unclear whether she is joking or not. &quot;-you will find I am arguably the pinnacle of horned health.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408170740";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081707719";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932686;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932686";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:20:" / ack, early enter.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408170749";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081707806";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932691;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932691";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:354:"/me scrunches her nose a little at the kiss, blushing but also reserved and does not return the gesture.[br]&quot;Brilliant...&quot;[br]Fortuna shakes her head. &quot;I have no allergies, other than one for stupid-&quot; She jokes, though it is unclear whether she is joking or not. &quot;-you will find I am arguably the pinnacle of horned health.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408170794";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081708246";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932698;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932698";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:640:"/me nodded. &quot;Alright then, coming right up.&quot; He said, donning his &#039;Kiss the Musician&#039; apron and beginning the late night meal. Sizzling and such could be heard from the kitchen, along with a quaint and spot on whistle of a classical song. &quot;So Fortuna, have you tried any Germane food at all? I have plenty of recipes from old Oma and Opa.&quot; He chuckled. Orchestra&#039;s grandparents loved to cook. Orchestra was passed down their cookbook not so long ago. He&#039;d come into the living room with the small, old notebook. &quot;Go ahead and take a look.&quot; He said with a grin before returning to the stove.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408171119";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081709865";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932699;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932699";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:303:"/me uses her magic to take the notebook and open it, hovering it in front of her face but not in such a way as to obscure her view of him.[br]&quot;I have not had very much of any kind of food, really... just what I like, which I find by sheer accident.&quot; She admits. &quot;A passion of yours?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408171236";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081712679";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932702;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932702";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:329:"/me shook his head. &quot;I am Germane. I try to keep traditions of my family alive. It&#039;s an honor thing. Simply cooking from their book keeps the memory of Oma and Opa alive.&quot; He said, closing his eyes for a moment before stirring around the stroganoff. &quot;Almost done! Anything you wanna try some other time?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408171371";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081712377";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932746;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932746";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:402:"&quot;Hmm...&quot; She listens and thinks, flipping slowly through the pages... &quot;Nothing leaps at me, but I am sure I would at least tolerate any given thing in this notebook.&quot; She offers. &quot;I am not an overly fussy eater.&quot; She says before gently placing the book down on the couch-side table before slinking down and laying lengthwise on the couch, comfortably and against a pillow.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408172033";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14081720643";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:932751;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"932751";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:330:"/me would come in, still wearing his apron as he sat down and passed a bowl of stroganoff and a fork to Fortuna. The meal was a saute of sour cream, noodles, onions, and mushrooms. The smell, though was good, still smelt a bit different then what normal Ponyville ponies ate. With a cheery smile, he took the first, familiar bite.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408172309";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7