ame_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084401526";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944535;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944535";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:486:"/me listened to the explanation of the omelette. Thinking of the weird folded egg pancake. &quot;Huh. Seems pretty odd... Do you... you know. Still put fruits and such inside of it? I don&#039;t think eggs go very good with sweets.&quot; He said, looking her back with almost the same eyes. Orchestra was still trying to match her gaze. Something she probably doesn&#039;t expect other ponies to do. &quot;So, all in all, do you like the stroganoff?&quot; He asked, taking another bite.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408440152";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084401534";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944592;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944592";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:196:"/me&#039;s eyes are half-closed, looking nowhere in particular as she eats.[br]&quot;Oh definitely, it&#039;s very good..&quot; She nods gently. &quot;Is violin the only instrument you play?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408441633";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084416729";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944596;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944596";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:687:"/me shook his head. &quot;No. Though it is the one I am best at. Most instruments in the string section I could play. Some better then others with the violin being my favorite.&quot; He explained. Taking his now empty bowl, he&#039;d take Fortuna&#039;s bowl if she finished as well. While in the kitchen, the stallion would pop his insulin pill. Quite embarrassing in front of guests. Especially Fortuna. He&#039;d look over the bar counter to the living room. &quot;Would you be up for a Bock?&quot; He&#039;d ask. &quot;If we are tasting a little bit of Germane tonight then might as well savor what most others recognize us for. An expertly brewed, germane imported, dark beer.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408442029";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084420304";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944603;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944603";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:272:"/me watches Orch from the couch, unphased by the pill-thing. She&#039;d seen it before.[br]&quot;Yeees, that sounds alright.&quot; She smiles a little, resting her head sideways against the back of the chair. &quot;I used to play the piano, briefly. Hated the thing.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408442235";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084422752";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944604;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944604";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:479:"/me rolled his eyes, agreeing with Fortuna. &quot;Oh yes. Pianos are simply horrid!&quot; He gave his own tastes. &quot;[i]Dink-a-dink-a-dink.[/i]&quot; He mocked, tapping his hooves on the counter. &quot;It takes a master to play one of those clunky things. Even then, they are vastly overrated.&quot; He poured two semi large steins, carrying his to the couch and motioning for Fortuna to pick hers up in her magic. Since no hands. Sitting down beside her, he raised his stein.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408442477";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084424782";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944607;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944607";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:244:"/me raises hers with a smirk, amused for a few reasons including but not limited to the hilariously stereotypical serving containers.[br]&quot;Heh... agreed, dear.&quot; She touches her stein to his before drawing it closer to her mouth to sip.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408442564";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084426043";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944632;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944632";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:516:"/me liked keeping his Opa&#039;s old steins around like he kept his Oma&#039;s old cookbook around. Clinking the tips together in a toast, he took a small swig of the dark beer. His spin shivering slightly as he grew a warm smile. The cold beer was strong in taste like most other germane dark beers. Though, the bock had a rich texture and aftertaste, leaving a strong start and a smooth yet distinct aftertaste for a short time. &quot;Maybe next time I could get some Doppelbock. Very strong stuff.&quot; He joked.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408442887";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084428879";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944633;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944633";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:280:"/me kind of just gives this awkward, glass-eyed straight-face upon tasting the stuff. She is quiet for a few seconds, then opens her mouth to speak only to cough. &quot;W-wow.&quot; She coughs again. &quot;... if I ever run out of oil for my lantern, I will be sure to call.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408442967";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084430073";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944642;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944642";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:295:"/me nodded. &quot;Bocks known for a gentle kick. Still, this is the weakest and most casual of bocks.~&quot; He smirked, taking a deeper swig. Drinking Bock was not something easy to get in to, but a treat for people who do. &quot;Like it? I have small barrels ported in from time to time.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408443112";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084431129";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944697;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944697";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:260:"&quot;It-&quot; She coughs again, once. &quot;-is worth another go. I will not have to be said that Fortuna gave up on anything.&quot; She insists before having a larger swill at it. To similar, but not identical effect. &quot;... better the second time.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408444026";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084440664";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944707;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944707";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:270:"/me chuckled. Honestly, it wasn&#039;t to terribly strong of a beer. Orchestra remembered chugging the stuff when he was twenty. &quot;Eh. It&#039;s probably just a Germane thing.~&quot; He teased. &quot;I am sure you prefer more pallet quenching drinks, huh love?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408444200";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084442009";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944718;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944718";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:178:"&quot;Kind of... I&#039;ve employed my alchemy kit to create interesting drinks on a few occasions.... honestly, I don&#039;t really know what I favour. Mojitos, I suppose?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408444338";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084443779";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944726;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944726";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:383:"/me remembered the last time Fortuna had six or seven to many mojitos. It was quite cute to be honest. &quot;You are a different person when drinking Mojitos, I can tell you that from experience.&quot; He chuckled, taking a few more swigs of his bock before setting the stein down. &quot;So, any interesting drinks you&#039;d like me to try?~&quot; He cooed with a cute little smile.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408444467";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084444677";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944734;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944734";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Fortuna";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"691";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:9:"Orchestra";s:4:"text";s:306:"/me blushes a little and hmms, placing her stein down on the table... she adjusts her position casually, placing her head on Orch&#039;s lap, her snout against his tummy and nuzzles in there a little to get comfortable. With a warm, long sigh, she shuts her eyes.[br]&quot;Well, certainly the mojito.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408444602";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c07af4";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084446420";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8ed7f3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944749;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944749";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10690";s:6:"handle";s:9:"Orchestra";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"791";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Fortuna";s:4:"text";s:384:"/me would lay back on the couch a bit more so Fortuna can rest her head easier. His hind hooves now kicked up on the coffee table. The red stallion ran a hoof tenderly through her hair, meeting her gaze with his gentle warm smile. &quot;I love you Fortuna.&quot; He&#039;d yawn. This evening&#039;s delights still resting in his head and the ware on him bringing his body to the same.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1408444866";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c12d15";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14084448668";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f01644";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:944760;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"944760";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1